{"tid":1513180,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「開心野」大家一齊將來點樣清算警隊！","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:25:45.000Z","uid":39703,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"68c72221ab42f89d06556bed5d92e4ed2a421c53","tid":1513180,"uid":39703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:18:00.000Z","msg":"係大家咁忙於要對抗呢個極權政府<br />\n相信大家都好攰好灰<br />\n但我相信我地會笑到最後 抗爭會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n而家我地一齊諗啲開心野！<br />\n就係成功左之後我地要點樣清算香港警察！<br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\n公開所有警察既個人資料<br />\n姓名 年齡 樣 身分證號碼 等等所有資料 <br />\n俾個個出街都認到佢係黑警<br />\n唔好俾佢地搵到工！<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n沒收所有福利<br />\n無宿舍 無公屋居屋 無綜援或任何資助<br />\n睇醫生去公立要收外國人價錢<br />\n不批任何護照簽證和移民 <br />\n不批貸款和信用卡 <br />\n不可安葬於公營骨灰翕位或墓地<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n禍必及妻兒！<br />\n此罰三代生效！<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗下可以點樣清算呢班仆街！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018d5708cb1b4d8641c1f59b7e66af6066c9d2da","tid":1513180,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAP